summary: An ordinance appropriating money from the general fund of the City of Seattle for the purpose of paying the amount awarded to the owner or owners of property taken or damaged in the condemnation case for the appropriation of a portion of Lot 13, Block 11, Renton's Addition to the City of Seattle, for street and highway purposes, as provided for by Ordinance No. 36585, Cause No. 119399 and repealing Section 2 of said Ordinance No. 26585.
